title: Episode 41 - Looking Ahead To Pyeongchang 2018
itunes:title: Episode 41 - Looking Ahead To Pyeongchang 2018
description: For the first time since the Rio games the entire gang of hosts are together as Ben, Colin & Jarrod discuss a variety of different things as we continue to push forward towards the next Winter Olympics in Pyeongchang next year! Through discussing various sports, getting the mascots names wrong and finding out what name Colin can come up with for Chumpy Pullin every five minutes, you'll be glad to have the boys back together once again!
